title: 2 Top Warren Buffett Stocks to Buy in 2023
description: The Oracle of Ohama, Warren Buffett, is known for many things.  Not the least of these is his long-held strategy of investing in robust, undervalued businesses in resilient industries with strong tailwinds to future growth -- and then building upon those positions over the years.  Buffett-led Berkshire Hathway (NYSE: BRK.A) (NYSE: BRK.B) has exhibited the strength of this simple philosophy time and time again.
